The '''Naboo Diplomatic Corps''' was a governmental organization set up by the [[Royal House of Naboo/Legends|Royal House of Naboo]] during the rule of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

The diplomatic corps was a branch of the [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] government based in [[Theed/Legends|Theed]], designed to provide diplomatic relations with other worlds in the [[Chommell sector/Legends|Chommell sector]] and beyond. [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] was the Ambassador of Naboo prior to the [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|Invasion of Naboo]], and later [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]] took up the position.

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the Naboo Diplomatic Corps made use of [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300 light freighters]].<ref name="SWG:JtL">''[[Star Wars Galaxies: Jump to Lightspeed]]''</ref>

